Project Description
A DotNetNuke Design Challenge skin package submitted to the "Modern Business" category by Exionyte Solutions. This package features 2 colors with 4 background styles & multiple containers. This skin and container set uses the Core DNN Navigation Provider.

The initial release of this HTML skin & container package requires DotNetNuke Core (Community or Pro) version 5.2.0 or greater.

A live demo can be seen @: http://skins.dotnetnuke.com/synapsebusiness
Originally contributed by: Exionyte Solutions
